    <h1>Cancellation and Refund Policy</h1>
    <p>At PIDANA Technologies Pvt Ltd, we strive to ensure customer satisfaction. This Cancellation and Refund Policy outlines the terms under which cancellations and refunds can be requested.</p>

    <h2>1. Cancellation Policy</h2>
    <p>
        - **Before Dispatch:** Customers may cancel their order within 24 hours of placing it or before the order is dispatched, whichever is earlier.<br />
        - To cancel your order, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@pidana.in">support@pidana.in</a> with your order details.<br />
        - **After Dispatch:** Orders that have already been dispatched cannot be canceled. Customers may initiate a return instead, as per our Return Policy.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Refund Policy</h2>
    <p>
        Refunds are applicable only under the following circumstances:<br />
        - The product is not delivered within the specified timeframe due to reasons within our control.<br />
        - The product delivered is defective or damaged and cannot be repaired or replaced.<br />
        - Service-related issues where the agreed-upon quality or timelines are not met.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Refund Process</h2>
    <p>
        To initiate a refund, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@pidana.in">support@pidana.in</a> with the following details:<br />
        - Order ID<br />
        - Reason for refund request<br />
        - Supporting documents (e.g., images of defective products, if applicable)<br />
        Refunds will be processed within **7-10 business days** after verification. Refunds will be credited to the original mode of payment unless specified otherwise.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Important Notes</h2>
    <p>
        - **Non-Refundable Items:** Customized or special-order products are non-refundable unless defective.<br />
        - **Shipping Costs:** Refunds do not include shipping fees unless the issue is due to our fault.<br />
        - **Return Condition:** Returned products must be unused, in original packaging, and include all accessories.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this policy, feel free to reach us at:</p>
    <p>
        Email: <a href="mailto:support@pidana.in">support@pidana.in</a><br />
        Phone: +91-XXXXXXXXXX
    </p>
